title New note(SPA)

note over Browser:
Type some text into the input field,
and click the save button.
end note

note over Browser:
Excute the form onsubmit event.
The event handler immediately calls 
the method e.preventDefault() to prevent
the default handling of form submit.
end note

note over Browser:
The new note adds to the notes list.
Then rerenders the node list on the page
and send the new note to the server.
end note


Browser->Server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over Server:
Update notes list
end note

Server-->Browser: Status Code: 201 Created